# Module: tf.contrib.lite



Defined in [`tensorflow/contrib/lite/python/lite.py`](https://www.github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r1.8/tensorflow/contrib/lite/python/lite.py).

TensorFlow Lite tooling helper functionality.

EXPERIMENTAL: APIs here are unstable and likely to change without notice.
